      "author": "pourmand1376",
      "description": "Screen Recorder Config: Xiaomi \r\nResolution: 800 * 480\r\nVideo Quality: 16 Mbps\r\nOrientation: Landscape\r\nSound Source: Mute\r\nFrame rate: 15fps\r\n\r\nConvert this to giff via ffmpeg:\r\n```\r\nffmpeg -i multiple_fonts_config.mp4 -filter_complex 'fps=15,scale=800:-1:flags=lanczos,split [o1] [o2];[o1] palettegen [p]; [o2] fifo [o3];[o3] [p] paletteuse' out.gif \r\n```",
